import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
import {
  Box,
  TextField,
  MenuItem,
  FormControl,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  // Divider,
  Chip,
} from "@mui/material";
import Divider from "@mui/material/Divider";
import { LoadingButton } from "@mui/lab";

const days = [...Array(32).keys()];
days.shift();

const months = [...Array(13).keys()];
months.shift();

const Register = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      component="div"
      sx={{
        display: "flex",
        flexDirection: "column",
        flexWrap: "wrap",
        maxWidth: 600,
        border: ".1px solid black",
        borderRadius: ".3rem",
      }}
      mt={12}
      ml="auto"
      mr="auto"
      p={2}
      gap={2}
    >
      <Typography variant="h3" fontWeight="bold">
        Creare cont
      </Typography>
      <Box component="form">
        <Grid
          container
          spacing={2}
          sx={{ alignItems: "center", justifyContent: "center" }}
        >
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Divider light style={{ width: "100%" }} textAlign="center">
              <Chip label="Cont" size="small" />
            </Divider>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField
                type="text"
                label="Nume"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
                required
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField
                type="email"
                label="Email"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
                required
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField
                type="password"
                label="Parolă"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
                required
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField
                type="password"
                label="Confirmare parolă"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
                required
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Divider light style={{ width: "100%" }} textAlign="center">
              <Chip label="Fizic" size="small" />
            </Divider>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField
                label="Sex"
                variant="outlined"
                select
                value=""
                size="small"
              >
                <MenuItem value=""></MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value="m">M</MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value="f">F</MenuItem>
              </TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={3}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField size="small" select value="" label="Zi">
                {days.map((day, i) => (
                  <MenuItem key={i} value={day}>
                    {day}
                  </MenuItem>
                ))}
              </TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={3}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField size="small" select value="" label="Luna">
                {months.map((month, i) => (
                  <MenuItem key={i} value={month}>
                    {month}
                  </MenuItem>
                ))}
              </TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField size="small" label="An"></TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField size="small" label="Înălțime (cm)"></TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl fullWidth>
              <TextField size="small" label="Greutate curentă (kg)"></TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
      <LoadingButton
        variant="contained"
        loadingPosition="center"
        sx={{
          fontSize: "1rem",
          alignSelf: "flex-start",
          textTransform: "capitalize",
          backgroundColor: "secondary.main",
          "&:hover": { backgroundColor: "secondary.main" },
        }}
      >
        Înregistrare
      </LoadingButton>
      <Typography
        variant="p"
        component="p"
        sx={{ fontSize: ".9rem", fontStyle: "italic" }}
      >
        Ai deja un cont? Conectează-te de
        <Typography color="red">
          <Link to="/login">aici</Link>!
        </Typography>
      </Typography>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Register;
